<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="go-out">go out</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>外出；(灯火等) 熄灭：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Perhaps we could go out to do some sightseeing together.
也许我们可以一起出去看看风景。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was in the middle of packing up my things when suddenly the power went out in the neighborhood.
我正在收拾东西的时候，整个街区突然停电了。</p></div>

<h3 id="go-out-put-out">辨析 go out, put out</h3>
<p>二者都和“熄灭”有关。<br />
<strong>go out ** 是不及物的短语动词，指由于某种原因熄灭。
</strong>put out ** 是及物的短语动词，指人为地使火、灯等熄灭。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Firemen soon put the fire out. 
消防队员很快就把火扑灭了。</p></div></div>